    <string name="title_about">About</string>
    <string name="about_text_app">Hi! My name is Jeroen and I developed this app during the first months after I decided that I wanted to adapt a vegan lifestyle. I found it annoying to browse websites in the store to find out whether products were vegan or not. With this app, I hope to support others in their quest for an animal-friendly lifestyle.</string>
    <string name="about_title_ingredients">Ingredient information</string>
    <string name="about_text_ingredients">All ingredient information has been manually constructed by searching the internet. A list like this will never be finished nor flawless. If you miss information or find an error, please let me know by sending an email to contactisitvegan@gmail.com.</string>
    <string name="about_title_barcode">Barcodes</string>
    <string name="about_text_barcode">When scanning barcodes, the online database of Open Food Facts is queried for the product\'s ingredient list. Open Food Facts is a food products database made by everyone, for everyone. Be aware that data might be incomplete or incorrect. For more information, visit <a href="https://world.openfoodfacts.org">openfoodfacts.org</a>.</string>
